Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.maze.tiles

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Door
    A door tile that can either be open (free) or closed (not free).
    ExitDoor
    A door tile that can only be opened if chap has collected a minimum number of chips (this will usually be all the chips in the level.) It blocks the way to the exit (is the exit lock).
    Free
    A free tile that actors (chap) can walk onto and interact with and can contain an item that can also be interacted with.
    LockedDoor
    A door tile that can be opened if chap has the matching key.
    Tile
    A tile of the board.
    TileInfo_Impl
    Implements the TileInfo class and contains the meta data on a tile (e.g Free or Door).
    Wall
    A wall tile that is not free and can never be walked onto or interacted with.
